    "description": "<strong>恐惧梦魇</strong> 是一款第一人称心理恐怖游戏，你将调查妹妹失踪的案件。找到妹妹和她团队留下的笔记，以揭示究竟发生了什么以及原因。<br>附注：过程并不愉快。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >噩梦般的挑战</h2></li></ul>面对越来越艰难的挑战，因为你面对的实体不断改变环境。直到现在，你还没有真正感受到恐惧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/4c2b1bc1e4c669a05724edb33411199c.poster.avif?t=1769442683\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/4c2b1bc1e4c669a05724edb33411199c.webm?t=1769442683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/4c2b1bc1e4c669a05724edb33411199c.mp4?t=1769442683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开秘密</h2></li></ul>你在寻找你的妹妹，而你最大的恐惧正成为现实。她进入了那座被禁止的废弃豪宅。探索这座豪宅及其周围环境，找出其中到底有什么真正不对劲的地方。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/698b1d709a488233bf77c7b2b2155b59.poster.avif?t=1769442683\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/698b1d709a488233bf77c7b2b2155b59.webm?t=1769442683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/698b1d709a488233bf77c7b2b2155b59.mp4?t=1769442683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感受恐怖</h2></li></ul>游戏采用了逼真的图形和沉浸式音效，但最重要的是，超自然实体的行为才真正带来恐怖感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/55db33d8e6ceb1e3731e3f6ef544b623.poster.avif?t=1769442683\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/55db33d8e6ceb1e3731e3f6ef544b623.webm?t=1769442683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196740/extras/55db33d8e6ceb1e3731e3f6ef544b623.mp4?t=1769442683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>免责声明</strong>: 如果你无法承受真正的恐怖，必须离开此页面。",
